1
00:00:45,640 --> 00:00:46,360
For over 20 years,

2
00:00:46,360 --> 00:00:47,890
what have I been living for?

3
00:00:49,440 --> 00:00:50,920
My identity is fake.

4
00:00:54,080 --> 00:00:54,880
Dan Pa.

5
00:00:55,880 --> 00:00:56,720
Even my birth,

6
00:00:56,720 --> 00:00:58,320
was it all calculated by you?

7
00:01:04,239 --> 00:01:06,840
Since he refuses to acknowledge you as his son,

8
00:01:07,280 --> 00:01:10,010
you don't need to acknowledge him as your father.

9
00:01:12,800 --> 00:01:14,800
Actually, I never dared to tell you.

10
00:01:15,440 --> 00:01:16,680
My father's death

11
00:01:19,320 --> 00:01:20,780
was also ordered by Dan Pa.

12
00:01:25,039 --> 00:01:25,840
So,

13
00:01:27,840 --> 00:01:29,560
when Uncle Dai died back then,

14
00:01:31,039 --> 00:01:32,440
he used the excuse

15
00:01:33,320 --> 00:01:35,780
of taking you and Auntie home to care for you,

16
00:01:37,600 --> 00:01:40,600
but actually it was to swallow the Dai family's power.

17
00:01:44,240 --> 00:01:46,500
Then my mother's death five years ago...

18
00:01:50,520 --> 00:01:53,320
I suspect my mother's death is also related to him.

19
00:02:01,960 --> 00:02:02,520
Ang Wei.

20
00:02:04,680 --> 00:02:05,540
The road ahead,

21
00:02:07,160 --> 00:02:08,520
let's walk it together.

22
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:27,079
Everyone,

23
00:02:27,760 --> 00:02:29,560
I gathered you all here today...

24
00:02:30,000 --> 00:02:31,730
I have an announcement to make.

25
00:02:33,880 --> 00:02:34,480
Come here.

26
00:02:37,800 --> 00:02:38,640
Ou Shaowen.

27
00:02:38,800 --> 00:02:40,800
What is he doing here at Sihai Group?

28
00:02:41,000 --> 00:02:43,860
I don't know. Looks like things are about to change.

29
00:02:53,120 --> 00:02:55,720
I have reached an agreement with Siam Group.

30
00:02:56,440 --> 00:02:59,240
The three shipping routes in the middle and upper reaches of Laeo

31
00:02:59,240 --> 00:03:01,120
will be operated by Siam Group,

32
00:03:02,200 --> 00:03:05,440
under the full management of Ou Shaowen.

33
00:03:06,840 --> 00:03:08,300
Thank you, foster father.

34
00:03:08,560 --> 00:03:09,880
I will not let you down.

35
00:03:20,560 --> 00:03:21,320
Uncle Danpa.

36
00:03:22,720 --> 00:03:23,920
Did you want to see me?

37
00:03:26,640 --> 00:03:27,640
It's very simple.

38
00:03:29,120 --> 00:03:30,880
Help me bring down Angwei.

39
00:03:32,160 --> 00:03:33,640
I'll let you have Dailing.

40
00:03:39,920 --> 00:03:41,840
If you take me as your godfather

41
00:03:42,360 --> 00:03:43,920
and bring down Angwei,

42
00:03:44,560 --> 00:03:47,360
Dailing will naturally listen to you.

43
00:03:56,680 --> 00:03:57,340
Godfather.

44
00:04:00,440 --> 00:04:01,080
Wait.

45
00:04:18,360 --> 00:04:18,920
Father.

46
00:04:20,720 --> 00:04:21,839
Since when did our Chen family's property

47
00:04:21,839 --> 00:04:22,840
fall into the hands

48
00:04:22,840 --> 00:04:23,920
of an outsider?

49
00:04:24,280 --> 00:04:25,080
An outsider?

50
00:04:26,160 --> 00:04:27,420
I have power and money.

51
00:04:27,920 --> 00:04:28,980
As for you, Ang Wei,

52
00:04:29,400 --> 00:04:30,400
look at yourself.

53
00:04:31,120 --> 00:04:32,840
Don't end up without

54
00:04:32,840 --> 00:04:34,900
even a single brick from Sihai Group.

55
00:04:35,560 --> 00:04:37,290
Will Dai Ling still be with you?

56
00:04:38,880 --> 00:04:39,680
Ou Shaowen.

57
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:40,680
I warn you,

58
00:04:41,720 --> 00:04:43,159
stay away from Dailing.

59
00:04:43,480 --> 00:04:45,720
If you dare to take this route today,

60
00:04:46,800 --> 00:04:48,730
I'll make you leave on a stretcher.

61
00:04:48,760 --> 00:04:49,960
Leave on a stretcher?

62
00:04:50,880 --> 00:04:52,320
Know your place.

63
00:04:52,880 --> 00:04:54,400
Who gets Dailing and the route

64
00:04:54,400 --> 00:04:55,880
is not up to you alone.

65
00:04:56,360 --> 00:04:57,600
You are now just a

66
00:04:58,240 --> 00:04:59,720
powerless,

67
00:05:00,240 --> 00:05:02,000
fatherless loser.

68
00:05:04,080 --> 00:05:04,880
I'll kill you.

69
00:05:05,160 --> 00:05:05,960
Do it.

70
00:05:06,840 --> 00:05:08,440
If you dare lay a finger on me,

71
00:05:08,680 --> 00:05:10,740
my adoptive father won't let you off.

72
00:05:11,560 --> 00:05:12,400
Enough.

73
00:05:14,080 --> 00:05:15,080
We are all family.

74
00:05:15,320 --> 00:05:16,480
Drawing guns on each other,

75
00:05:16,480 --> 00:05:17,480
what a disgrace.

76
00:05:18,240 --> 00:05:19,170
Put the gun down.

77
00:05:30,000 --> 00:05:31,200
By the way, Angwei.

78
00:05:31,680 --> 00:05:35,000
Hand over Tan Palace to the group tomorrow.

79
00:05:35,880 --> 00:05:37,940
I'll give you a few profitable docks.

80
00:05:38,080 --> 00:05:39,740
Once you stabilize the docks,

81
00:05:39,960 --> 00:05:41,290
I'll give it back to you.

82
00:05:51,960 --> 00:05:52,800
Alright.

83
00:05:53,440 --> 00:05:54,170
Young people

84
00:05:54,440 --> 00:05:55,440
have bad tempers.

85
00:05:55,760 --> 00:05:56,760
Let's continue.

86
00:05:58,520 --> 00:05:59,180
Godfather.

87
00:06:00,760 --> 00:06:02,360
I will put out Ang Wei's fire,

88
00:06:02,920 --> 00:06:03,640
little

89
00:06:04,560 --> 00:06:05,680
by little.

90
00:06:09,120 --> 00:06:10,450
Let's toast, everyone.

91
00:06:11,120 --> 00:06:11,680
Come,

92
00:06:11,680 --> 00:06:12,240
cheers.

93
00:06:12,240 --> 00:06:12,800
Come.

94
00:06:38,840 --> 00:06:41,100
Danpa completely trusts Ou Shaowen now.

95
00:06:42,080 --> 00:06:43,920
He wants to take back the entertainment city

96
00:06:43,920 --> 00:06:45,050
and give me the dock.

97
00:06:46,080 --> 00:06:47,140
The dock's profits

98
00:06:47,200 --> 00:06:49,440
are much higher than those of the entertainment city.

99
00:06:49,440 --> 00:06:50,159
Why would Danpa

100
00:06:50,159 --> 00:06:52,290
give you the most profitable project?

101
00:06:52,600 --> 00:06:54,280
Something is definitely wrong.

102
00:06:54,280 --> 00:06:56,720
I have been running Tan Palace for a long time.

103
00:06:56,720 --> 00:06:58,159
His taking it back now

104
00:06:58,880 --> 00:07:01,840
is nothing but an attempt to shake my foundation in Sihai,

105
00:07:01,840 --> 00:07:04,240
and eliminate my informants in Tan Palace.

106
00:07:04,680 --> 00:07:06,280
What are you going to do then?

107
00:07:09,080 --> 00:07:11,010
We'll find out when we go tomorrow.

108
00:07:11,080 --> 00:07:12,080
That's too risky.

109
00:07:12,640 --> 00:07:14,160
Danpa is clearly luring you with benefits.

110
00:07:14,160 --> 00:07:15,320
He's up to no good.

111
00:07:18,800 --> 00:07:20,200
You are worried about me.

112
00:07:23,760 --> 00:07:25,440
You treat him as your adoptive father,

113
00:07:25,440 --> 00:07:26,900
but he treats you as a pawn.

114
00:07:27,560 --> 00:07:28,480
Even so,

115
00:07:28,480 --> 00:07:31,010
are you still willing to be a pawn in his hands?

116
00:07:34,840 --> 00:07:35,800
Don't worry.

117
00:07:36,720 --> 00:07:37,880
He won't kill me.

118
00:07:39,080 --> 00:07:39,760
After all,

119
00:07:40,240 --> 00:07:41,400
if he kills me,

120
00:07:42,159 --> 00:07:44,290
it will chill the hearts of the elders.

121
00:07:46,720 --> 00:07:49,120
Danpa now has Ou Shaowen as his adopted son.

122
00:07:50,200 --> 00:07:51,000
And Ou Shaowen

123
00:07:51,560 --> 00:07:53,760
is not the same Ou Shaowen from the past.

124
00:07:53,760 --> 00:07:56,159
They definitely won't go easy on you again.

125
00:08:02,480 --> 00:08:03,610
Then I will bet on it.

126
00:08:06,120 --> 00:08:08,580
I bet Ou Shaowen is still the same Ou Shaowen.

127
00:08:14,000 --> 00:08:15,200
Then I'll go with you.

128
00:08:15,320 --> 00:08:15,920
No.

129
00:08:17,400 --> 00:08:18,520
It's too dangerous.

130
00:08:18,520 --> 00:08:19,250
You can't go.

131
00:08:19,280 --> 00:08:20,120
It's precisely because it's dangerous

132
00:08:20,120 --> 00:08:21,200
that I must go.

133
00:08:22,280 --> 00:08:24,140
I'm not discussing this with you.

134
00:08:27,360 --> 00:08:28,360
Five years ago,

135
00:08:29,720 --> 00:08:31,320
I already lost you once.

136
00:08:32,960 --> 00:08:34,480
I can't lose you again.

137
00:08:36,240 --> 00:08:37,280
I can go,

138
00:08:38,159 --> 00:08:39,080
but you can't.

139
00:08:40,039 --> 00:08:40,840
I promise you,

140
00:08:41,799 --> 00:08:43,200
I'll get out of this in one piece

141
00:08:43,200 --> 00:08:44,400
and come home safely.

142
00:08:46,800 --> 00:08:48,400
I can protect you in the dark.

143
00:08:48,560 --> 00:08:49,760
I just need to see you.

144
00:08:57,000 --> 00:08:58,330
Wait for me to come back.

145
00:09:01,920 --> 00:09:02,800
Come back safely.
